  {
    "id": "200662070448291_1562186745916931",
    "message": "It's Ohio On Tap Week, and we're celebrating with From the Heart, vol 6,  a golden summer lager in the English style brewed with wheat & a special hop blend lending balance & hints of nectarines & citrus.  Designed by our very own Kevin Ely, this beer is a love letter to Ohio’s craft beer scene benefitting the Ohio Craft Brewers Association.  In a statewide collaboration, more than 60 Ohio breweries will be releasing Vol. 6 this week–each with their own twist.  Try them all to find a favorite.  #ohioontap #fromtheheart #summerlager #sessionbeer #drinkbeerbreweredhere \nOhio Craft Beer @ohiocraftbeer Northeast Ohio Craft Beverage News @neo_craft_brewery_news Ohio On Tap @ohioontapapp",
